lead_paragraph: Jay Cutler threw for 252 yards and a touchdown and Jordan Howard ran for 153 yards and a score as the Chicago Bears beat the Minnesota Vikings 20-10 at Soldier Field on Monday.

headline.print_headline: Bears Beat Vikings as Quarterback Cutler Makes Winning Return
